        "description": "**IMPORTANT**: This endpoint uses the Platform API (different base URL).\n\nRegisters fee-distribution settings for a newly created LBP mint. This is required on Solana to adjust Fee Builder rerouting\n\n**Required fields**\n\n- `chainId` - Must match the LBP chain ID\n    \n- `address` - Mint address from create-lbp response\n    \n- Percent fields should sum reasonably (with `customFees[].percent`)\n    \n- `feeDistributionPayoutKind` - `SOL` or `TOKEN`\n    \n\n**Response**:\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"transaction\": \"<base64>\",\n  \"blockhash\": \"...\",\n  \"lastValidBlockHeight\": 0\n}\n\n ```"
